      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight mb-6">Invisalign Insurance Coverage</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-8 text-lg max-w-3xl">Invisalign is often handled through orthodontic benefits, which can be different from regular dental coverage.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
